Package: python-django-markitup
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python-django (>= 1.1)
Description: A reusable application for end-to-end markup handling
 A Django reusable application for end-to-end markup handling.
 Includes integration with the MarkItUp universal markup editor
 (http://markitup.jaysalvat.com/) via a form widget, template tags,
 and AJAX preview.
 .
 Supports Markdown and Textile out of the box, easy to switch to custom
 MarkItUp! sets/skins and custom AJAX preview. Also includes MarkupField
 for transparent database storage of pre-rendered markup.
